{"tid":499584,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴打都失去左人生既熱情？","createTime":"2017-12-15T03:45:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-15T05:33:08.000Z","uid":123335,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1d0729779ac95e3082dc67eaebfe443693745b66","tid":499584,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T03:45:42.000Z","msg":"小時候，所有野都係第一次見識<br />\n所以往往都對個世界充滿興奮<br />\ne.g. 第一次同女仔有身體接觸，第一次拍拖，第一次去日本，第一次 ....etc <br />\n<br />\n但係人越大，<br />\n好多野都見過，好多路都走過 <br />\n已經不再新奇有趣 <br />\n成日都心諗：「好出奇咩？」<br />\n「係咁架啦」<br />\n<br />\n加上出到黎社會，見識多人性既黑暗面<br />\n更加慢慢開始對個世界熱情不再<br />\n個腦開始充滿住「利益」「互利」「弱肉強食」..etc 字眼 <br />\n<br />\n家陣基本上<br />\n星期1-5返工d錢大部份就用黎供樓 (迷你單位) <br />\n放工就飲下酒麻醉自己<br />\n<br />\n對住個世界<br />\n有時真係唔想咁清醒"},{"pid":"aba50f552dad5451bae71d4c5c79942a8b3f0fc3","tid":499584,"uid":16767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T03:46:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b10e0eb6e4830849ff01395545a2b2747592783","tid":499584,"uid":115189,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T03:48:27.000Z","msg":"當新奇又驚訝嘅事都變成負擔<br />\n<br />\n仲有咩熱情可言"},{"pid":"ee222f1793ab8ee72b2b6832ffaa6b1abeeb8818","tid":499584,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T03:48:44.000Z","msg":"agree 樓主...<br />\n我日日都在數日子..<br />\n唔想再返工"},{"pid":"b1c24c4c4caeef41c4f58c3d4256bdc14cd985ef","tid":499584,"uid":25614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T03:49:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01054120e9c14c766717ad0962290bca8436b23f","tid":499584,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T03:56:16.000Z","msg":"巴打，我想改變<br />\n我可以點？"},{"pid":"7f8b34fdf8bcdaba13696331f1a716a3d7d10bd9","tid":499584,"uid":25614,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T03:57:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打，我想改變